Package: icreport
Title: Tools for creating a visual summary of matrix decomposition results.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Jinhyun", "Ju", email = "jinhyun.ju@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: icreport is a package for exploratory data analysis for gene
    expression data. ICA and PCA can be performed on expression data
    with simple code and comprehensive summary reports can be generated.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Imports:
    MASS,
    grid,
    gtools,
    ggplot2,
    mclust,
    parallel,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    testthat
